arker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20220622104135-2axiigh"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220622104135-y7zq56v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622104135-y7zq56v","updated":"20220622104322"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一个动态代理类代理的是一个接口，一般就是对应的一类业务"}]}]},{"ID":"20220622104322-fo7othy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20220622104322-fo7othy","updated":"20220622104343"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220622104322-qmy2dem","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622104322-qmy2dem","updated":"20220622104343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一个动态代理类可以代理多个类，只要是实现了同一个接口即可"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220622104024-5qszgun","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220622104024-5qszgun","updated":"20220622104355"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"AOP"}]},{"ID":"20220622104406-akw8oq1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220622104406-akw8oq1","updated":"20220622104431"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是aop"}]},{"ID":"20220622104434-zezx6dc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622104434-zezx6dc","updated":"20220622104440"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220622104440-u4fv0vu.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220622104452-6kvsumn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622104452-6kvsumn","updated":"20220622104453"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220622104452-yyxnfqg.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220622105742-7ov3vkd","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220622105742-7ov3vkd","updated":"20220622105750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用Spring实现Aop"}]},{"ID":"20220622105751-zm815d5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622105751-zm815d5","updated":"20220622143141"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.导入依赖"}]},{"ID":"20220622105804-3hb6b09","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622105804-3hb6b09","updated":"20220622105820"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eG1s"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"        \u003cdependency\u003e\n            \u003cgroupId\u003eorg.aspectj\u003c/groupId\u003e\n            \u003cartifactId\u003easpectjweaver\u003c/artifactId\u003e\n            \u003cversion\u003e1.9.4\u003c/version\u003e\n        \u003c/dependency\u003e\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622105820-ahbt3q3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622105820-ahbt3q3","updated":"20220622143144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.使用Spring的API接口"}]},{"ID":"20220622143153-mcfwl6u","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622143153-mcfwl6u"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eG1s"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\u003c?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?\u003e\n\u003cbeans xmlns=\"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans\"\n       xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n       xmlns:aop=\"http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop\"\n       xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans\n        https://www.springframework.org/schema/beans/spring-beans.xsd\n        http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop\n        https://www.springframework.org/schema/aop/spring-aop.xsd\"\u003e\n\n        \u003c!--注册bean--\u003e\n    \u003cbean id=\"userService\" class=\"com.Xia.service.UserServiceImpl\"/\u003e\n    \u003cbean id=\"log\" class=\"com.Xia.log.log\"/\u003e\n    \u003cbean id=\"afterLog\" class=\"com.Xia.log.AfterLog\"/\u003e\n\n    \u003c!--配置aop:需要导入aop约束--\u003e\n    \u003caop:config\u003e\n        \u003c!--切入点:expression:表达式，execution（要执行的位置! ****）--\u003e\n        \u003caop:pointcut id=\"pointcut\" expression=\"execution(* com.Xia.service.UserServiceImpl.*(..))\"/\u003e\n\n        \u003c!--执行环绕增加--\u003e\n        \u003caop:advisor advice-ref=\"log\" pointcut-ref=\"pointcut\"/\u003e\n        \u003caop:advisor advice-ref=\"afterLog\" pointcut-ref=\"pointcut\"/\u003e\n\n\n    \u003c/aop:config\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003c/beans\u003e"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622143156-kokdqjz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622143156-kokdqjz","updated":"20220622143201"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.接口"}]},{"ID":"20220622143206-p8onpom","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622143206-p8onpom","updated":"20220622143224"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"package com.Xia.service;\n\npublic interface UserService {\n    public void add();\n    public void delete();\n    public void update();\n    public void select();\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622143215-tcbbgao","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622143215-tcbbgao","updated":"20220622143218"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.实现类"}]},{"ID":"20220622143219-1995a9t","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622143219-1995a9t","updated":"20220622143225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"package com.Xia.service;\n\npublic class UserServiceImpl implements UserService{\n    public void add(){\n        System.out.println(\"增加了一个用户\");\n    };\n    public void delete(){\n        System.out.println(\"删除了一个用户\");\n    };\n    public void update(){\n        System.out.println(\"更新了一个用户\");\n    };\n    public void select(){\n        System.out.println(\"查询了一个用户\");\n    };\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622143227-3ics1je","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622143227-3ics1je","updated":"20220622143239"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.日志"}]},{"ID":"20220622143244-f0u8ym9","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622143244-f0u8ym9"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"package com.Xia.log;\n\nimport org.springframework.aop.MethodBeforeAdvice;\n\nimport java.lang.reflect.Method;\n\npublic class log implements MethodBeforeAdvice {\n\n    //method:要执行的目标对象的方法\n    //args：参数\n    //target：目标对象\n    @Override\n    public void before(Method method, Object[] args, Object target) throws Throwable {\n        System.out.println(target.getClass().getName()+\"的\"+method.getName()+\"被执行了\");\n    }\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622143237-96n5sxh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622143237-96n5sxh","updated":"20220622143257"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"service日志"}]},{"ID":"20220622143251-0wixzer","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622143251-0wixzer"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"package com.Xia.log;\n\nimport org.springframework.aop.AfterReturningAdvice;\n\nimport java.lang.reflect.Method;\n\npublic class AfterLog implements AfterReturningAdvice {\n    @Override\n    public void afterReturning(Object returnValue, Method method, Object[] args, Object target) throws Throwable {\n        System.out.println(\"执行了\"+method.getName()+\"方法，返回结果为\"+returnValue);\n    }\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622143259-rkpq54i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622143259-rkpq54i","updated":"20220622143307"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.测试类"}]},{"ID":"20220622143311-ge22syc","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622143311-ge22syc","updated":"20220622143343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import com.Xia.service.UserService;\nimport com.Xia.service.UserServiceImpl;\nimport org.springframework.context.ApplicationContext;\nimport org.springframework.context.support.ClassPathXmlApplicationContext;\n\npublic class MyTest {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        ApplicationContext context = new ClassPathXmlApplicationContext(\"applicationContext.xml\");\n\n        //动态代理的是接口\n        UserService userService = (UserService) context.getBean(\"userService\");\n\n        userService.select();\n    }\n}\n\n/*结果\ncom.Xia.service.UserServiceImpl的select被执行了\n查询了一个用户\n执行了select方法，返回结果为null\n*/\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622143314-g911f1x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622143314-g911f1x","updated":"20220622152739"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220622152739-niv6le8.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220622152743-fdboevm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220622152743-fdboevm","updated":"20220622153034"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自定义实现Aop【主要是切面定义】"}]},{"ID":"20220622152755-mqpavr6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622152755-mqpavr6","updated":"20220622152825"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"切入点定义"}]},{"ID":"20220622152826-a2t1gs3","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622152826-a2t1gs3","updated":"20220622152958"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eG1s"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\u003c?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?\u003e\n\u003cbeans xmlns=\"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans\"\n       xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n       xmlns:aop=\"http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop\"\n       xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans\n        https://www.springframework.org/schema/beans/spring-beans.xsd\n        http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop\n        https://www.springframework.org/schema/aop/spring-aop.xsd\"\u003e\n\n        \u003c!--注册bean--\u003e\n    \u003cbean id=\"userService\" class=\"com.Xia.service.UserServiceImpl\"/\u003e\n    \u003cbean id=\"log\" class=\"com.Xia.log.log\"/\u003e\n    \u003cbean id=\"afterLog\" class=\"com.Xia.log.AfterLog\"/\u003e\n\n    \u003c!--配置aop:需要导入aop约束--\u003e\n\n        \u003cbean id=\"diy\" class=\"com.Xia.diy.DiyPointCut\"/\u003e\n\n        \u003caop:config\u003e\n            \u003c!--自定义切面，ref 要引用的类--\u003e\n            \u003caop:aspect ref=\"diy\"\u003e\n                \u003c!--切入点--\u003e\n                \u003caop:pointcut id=\"point\" expression=\"execution(* com.Xia.service.UserServiceImpl.*(..))\"/\u003e\n                \u003c!--通知--\u003e\n                \u003caop:before method=\"before\" pointcut-ref=\"point\"/\u003e\n                \u003caop:after method=\"after\" pointcut-ref=\"point\"/\u003e\n\n            \u003c/aop:aspect\u003e\n        \u003c/aop:config\u003e\n\n\u003c/beans\u003e\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622152830-vzeq8r2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622152830-vzeq8r2","updated":"20220622152851"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实现类"}]},{"ID":"20220622152855-ghhuq9g","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622152855-ghhuq9g"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"package com.Xia.diy;\n\npublic class DiyPointCut {\n    public void before(){\n        System.out.println(\"====方法执行前====\");\n    }\n    public void after(){\n        System.out.println(\"====方法执行后====\");\n    }\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622152902-lby8byk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622152902-lby8byk","updated":"20220622152904"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"测试类"}]},{"ID":"20220622152905-wequgjz","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622152905-wequgjz"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"public class MyTest {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        ApplicationContext context = new ClassPathXmlApplicationContext(\"applicationContext.xml\");\n\n        //动态代理的是接口\n        UserService userService = (UserService) context.getBean(\"userService\");\n\n        userService.select();\n    }\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622153105-znnpk01","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220622153105-znnpk01","updated":"20220622153129"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用注解实现Aop类"}]},{"ID":"20220622160655-o26zzj3","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622160655-o26zzj3","updated":"20220622160700"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eG1s"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\u003c?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?\u003e\n\u003cbeans xmlns=\"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans\"\n       xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n       xmlns:aop=\"http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop\"\n       xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans\n        https://www.springframework.org/schema/beans/spring-beans.xsd\n        http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop\n        https://www.springframework.org/schema/aop/spring-aop.xsd\"\u003e\n\n        \u003c!--注册bean--\u003e\n    \u003cbean id=\"userService\" class=\"com.Xia.service.UserServiceImpl\"/\u003e\n    \u003cbean id=\"log\" class=\"com.Xia.log.log\"/\u003e\n    \u003cbean id=\"afterLog\" class=\"com.Xia.log.AfterLog\"/\u003e\n\n        \u003cbean id=\"annotationPointCut\" class=\"com.Xia.diy.AnnotationPointCut\"/\u003e\n        \u003caop:aspectj-autoproxy/\u003e\n\u003c/beans\u003e\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622160709-choqqsu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622160709-choqqsu","updated":"20220622160725"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实现类"}]},{"ID":"20220622160726-9hx2uw9","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220622160726-9hx2uw9","updated":"20220622160729"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"package com.Xia.diy;\n\nimport org.aspectj.lang.annotation.After;\nimport org.aspectj.lang.annotation.Aspect;\nimport org.aspectj.lang.annotation.Before;\n\n@Aspect //标注这个类是一个切面\npublic class AnnotationPointCut {\n    @Before(\"execution(* com.Xia.service.UserServiceImpl.*(..))\")\n    public void before(){\n        System.out.println(\"====方法执行前====\");\n    }\n    @After(\"execution(* com.Xia.service.UserServiceImpl.*(..))\")\n    public void after(){\n        System.out.println(\"====方法执行后====\");\n    }\n\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220622161023-mg0cv4r","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220622161023-mg0cv4r","updated":"20220622161108"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"整合Mybatis"}]},{"ID":"20220622161110-uygms7a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220622161110-uygms7a"}}]}